  "content": "\n \n \n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-wrap-style: initial;color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">①项目：GLM-4.5</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"553\" data-imgfileid=\"100015403\" data-ratio=\"1.0072859744990892\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"549\" data-width=\"549\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=74e4914f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxPLdicJfSo550EUxiaPhZG7JlHJgXMzMItP1Zto0hes0tuqa3d7p41Uvic4Jicq4ic6XHsG0apwA0vtmQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">★</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">GLM-4.5是由Z.ai设计的开源大语言模型，专为智能智能体应用而开发。该模型拥有355B总参数和32B活跃参数，支持推理、编码和智能体功能。</span>GLM-4.5提供思考模式和非思考模式，以满足复杂推理和即时响应的需求。其开源版本包括基础模型、混合推理模型及FP8版本，允许商业和二次开发使用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/glm-4-5\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/glm-4-5</a></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-wrap-style: initial;color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">②项目：Wan2.2</span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39076154806491886\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"801\" data-width=\"801\" data-height=\"313\" data-imgfileid=\"100015405\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=795e3cc1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxPLdicJfSo550EUxiaPhZG7JNIAMDKzqQAVLs6e2wb1v1wKjzzYtWLNjOQSIxkTvIxib9Dky85fne6g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\">★<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Wan2.2-TI2V-5B是一个先进的大规模视频生成模型，支持文本到视频和图像到视频的生成。</span>该模型采用Mixture-of-Experts架构，能够在保持计算成本不变的情况下扩大模型容量。Wan2.2通过精心策划的美学数据，实现了可控的电影级风格生成，支持720P分辨率和24fps的视频输出，适用于工业和学术研究。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/wan2-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/wan2-2</a></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-wrap-style: initial;color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">③项目：HunyuanWorld 1.0</span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"463\" data-imgfileid=\"100015407\" data-ratio=\"0.5845959595959596\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"792\" data-width=\"792\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f801a89d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxPLdicJfSo550EUxiaPhZG7JTgN01Wxicojhrs69ptYD2iaPnpPyp1u7gts7McVDuCjSV4QlIA8wqLpw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">★HunyuanWorld 1.0 是一个创新的框架，旨在从文本或图像生成沉浸式、可探索和交互的3D世界。</span>该项目结合了视频和3D方法的优点，通过全景世界代理提供360°沉浸体验，支持网格导出以兼容现有计算机图形管道，并通过解耦的对象表示增强交互性。其核心是语义分层的3D网格表示，利用全景图像作为360°世界代理进行语义感知的世界分解和重建，广泛应用于虚拟现实、物理模拟、游戏开发和互动内容创作。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hunyuanworld-1-0\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hunyuanworld-1-0</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-wrap-style: initial;color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">①项目：siiRL</span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.61090458488228\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"807\" data-width=\"807\" data-height=\"493\" data-imgfileid=\"100015404\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=795b2998&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxPLdicJfSo550EUxiaPhZG7JwD0y5J0dkwIAhLyY4icm5icj0sbqqhmvkaIXZetn8ib4X44xWUnROqcSw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">★siiRL是一个创新的、完全分布式的强化学习框架，旨在突破LLM后训练</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">中的扩展瓶颈。</span>由</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\">上海创新研究院的研究人员开发，siiRL解决了限制当前最先进系统的关键性能瓶颈。通过消除其他框架中常见的集中控制器，siiRL实现了近线性扩展性、显著的吞吐量提升以及前所未有的灵活性，适用于基于RL的LLM开发。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/siirl\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/siirl</a></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-wrap-style: initial;color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">②项目：Data Whisperer</span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"615\" data-imgfileid=\"100015406\" data-ratio=\"0.8156498673740054\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"754\" data-width=\"754\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b424b4e6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxPLdicJfSo550EUxiaPhZG7JtMO6R1FVcPHZ9IJaPZaGmIctvfpM0tDibTUbtNtXLzwC27xzzbvEO5A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">★Data Whisperer是一个用于任务特定大语言模型（LLM）微调的数据选择工具。</span>通过少样本上下文学习，该项目旨在提高数据选择的效率。项目提供了一种参考实现，能够在不同的数据集和模型配置下进行实验，以优化模型的微调过程。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&